To enable namespace and subnamespaces privileges:
Log on to the computer you want to monitor with an administrator account.
Navigate to Start > Control Panel > Administrative Tools > Computer Management > Services and Applications. You need to switch to the Classic View of the Control Panel to use this navigation path.
Click WMI Control, and then right-click and select Properties.
Select the Security tab, and then expand Root and click CIMV2.
Click Security and then select the user account used to access this computer and ensure you grant the following permissions:
Enable Account
Remote Enable

